### Start Research Podcast Workflow
POST http://localhost:8080/workflows/research-podcast
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "podcast_name": "AI Security Voice",
  "host_name": "Test Host",
  "participants": [],
  "dialogue_max_rounds": 4,
  "output_directory": "output",
  "audio_model": "eleven_flash_v2_5"
}

### Check Workflow State
GET http://localhost:8080/workflows/<instance_id>

### Wait for Completion (30 minutes timeout)
GET http://localhost:8080/workflows/<instance_id>/wait?timeout=1800
